column5: My party will be going to the east arm the last week of June. Staying at the Fisheries Resort (third year in a row). Anyone have a fishing report? We target pike, smallies and eyes. Thanks in advance!
Explosive fishing for pike in bays and walleyes on 20' deep humps No smallies? Pre spawn>>>Spawn maybe??? Good luckLets hear it guys.
Fisheries Resort,is a great choice.The lake level is low but the fishing has been great.Go to your regular spots and fish about twenty feet further away.you will have a great time.
No Smallies? They got to be somewhere?:(
Lotsa Wallys no Smallies coudn't find them???Lets hear from others who have been up.

had some friends at the cottage last week of may. hammered the bass at reef point husky jerks worked well.four and a half lb was the biggest and lots of threes.they also tangled with some nasty big pike in same area.crapi were found in black stergeon bay landing some nice fourteen inchers. good luck you going to have a great trip.
